819
01:35:21.346 --> 01:35:24.766
Yes. I have connections.

820
01:35:26.476 --> 01:35:28.061
Okay. The PI N number's 4747.

821
01:35:28.103 --> 01:35:29.688
Okay. The PI N number's 4747.

