881
01:44:12.961 --> 01:44:16.631
They stick it in their body.
They tuck it up their rectum.

882
01:44:16.756 --> 01:44:19.968
You familiar with that?
This... Look at me.

883
01:44:20.093 --> 01:44:22.846
Pencil detonator.

884
01:44:22.970 --> 01:44:26.683
Timer. used as a receiver-transmitter.

885
01:44:26.766 --> 01:44:29.811
C-4. Highly explosive.

886
