Four minutes and 20 seconds.
Are you sure?

902
01:45:34.876 --> 01:45:37.712
Okay.

903
01:45:37.837 --> 01:45:41.048
I got all the time in the world.
You don't. but I do.

904
01:45:41.174 --> 01:45:43.926
- Hey. relax. relax. buddy.
- I'm relaxed.

905
