- Come on.

943
01:47:59.938 --> 01:48:04.359
- Thirty-five.
- A last wish. please. Please.

944
01:48:04.484 --> 01:48:09.698
Last wish?
I wish you had more time.

945
01:48:09.823 --> 01:48:13.910
- Hey! Hey. hey!

946
01:50:16.408 --> 01:50:20.036
