- Whose account is it?

951
01:50:30.839 --> 01:50:34.926
Jordan Kalfus. and it looks like
U. S. Deposits and withdrawals.

952
01:50:35.051 --> 01:50:37.012
Give me the same thing
on Samuel Ramos.

953
01:50:37.095 --> 01:50:40.807
Samuel Ramos. That's it?

954
01:50:40.932 --> 01:50:42.642
- That's it.
- Okay.

955
01:51:17.885 --> 01:51:19.804
Gracias.

956
01:51:28.229 --> 01:51:31.858
- Creasy.
- Samuel.

957
01:51:31.983 --> 01:51:33.985
Honey?

958
01:51:37.572 --> 01:51:39.950
What's going on?

959
01:51:41.742 --> 01:51:45.789
That's what I wanna know.
What is going on?

960
01:51:48.249 --> 01:51:51.127
Huh. Sam?

961
01:51:51.253 --> 01:51:53.463
I'm gonna ask your wife a couple
of questions. okay?

962
01:51:53.546 --> 01:51:56.507
You move...

963
01:51:56.591 --> 01:51:58.635
you make one sound...

964
01:51:58.760 --> 01:52:01.846
I'll snatch the life right outta you.
you understand?

965
01:52:09.145 --> 01:52:11.856
What happened. Lisa. hmm?

966
01:52:11.940 --> 01:52:13.858
Were you in on this?

967
01:52:13.942 --> 01:52:18.113
