968
01:52:18.238 --> 01:52:21.741
You know what I'm talking about... Pita's
kidnapping. her death. Were you a part of it?

969
01:52:21.866 --> 01:52:25.161
- Pita got killed because the ransom got stolen.
- Shut up!

970
01:52:26.705 --> 01:52:29.082
Yeah. the money was stolen.
You're right. He's right.

971
01:52:29.165 --> 01:52:32.711
The money was stolen by Victor Fuentes.
How much was stolen though. huh?

972
01:52:32.794 --> 01:52:35.797
- $2. 5 million. right?
- What are you talking about?

973
01:52:35.922 --> 01:52:39.050
He knows what I'm talking about.
$2. 5 million. That's what Victor got. isn't it?

974
01:52:39.133 --> 01:52:42.136
- What are you talking about?
- 2. 5 million.

975
01:52:42.261 --> 01:52:44.555
2. 5 million to your lawyer
Jordan Kalfus...

976
01:52:44.639 --> 01:52:47.767
that he put in an account in the Cayman
Islands. but he won't get a chance to spend it.

977
01:52:51.145 --> 01:52:53.440
What happened to the other five. Sam?

978
01:52:53.564 --> 01:52:56.484
Huh? That's 2. 5. 2. 5.
What is five from 10?

979
01:52:56.609 --> 01:52:59.112
That's five. What happened
to the other five. Sam? Tell your wife.

980
01:52:59.237 --> 01:53:01.656
- It's your chance to talk.
What happened to the other five?

981
01:53:01.781 --> 01:53:03.116
- You got a wife. Creasy?
- No. I don't have a wife.

982
01:53:03.241 --> 01:53:05.993
Then you'll never know how hard
it could be to tell your wife the truth.

983
01:53:06.119 --> 01:53:08.329
No. you have a wife!
You tell me what happened!

984
01:53:08.454 --> 01:53:10.582
It was in this room
that my father prayed.

985
01:53:10.665 --> 01:53:13.376
- I don't give a fuck about your fucking father!
- My father prayed.

986
01:53:13.501 --> 01:53:17.380
He prayed that his gambling debts and his
infidelities would be forgiven right in this room.

987
01:53:17.505 --> 01:53:20.174
- Samuel! I love you!
- What. Lisa?

988
01:53:20.300 --> 01:53:24.095
- Tell me the truth.
- I didn't inherit a kingdom! That's the truth!

989
01:53:24.179 --> 01:53:27.098
You wanna know the truth?
I inherited his debt and his mess.

990
01:53:27.181 --> 01:53:30.101
- I inherited his lawyer Jordan...
- You tell me what happened to my baby!

991
01:53:30.184 --> 01:53:32.771
Say it! Say it! Say it!

992
01:53:32.854 --> 01:53:35.482
Say it! Say it! Be a fucking man!

993
01:53:39.318 --> 01:53:41.738
Jordan told me she'd sit in a room...

994
01:53:41.863 --> 01:53:44.240
and watch cartoons all day...

995
01:53:44.365 --> 01:53:47.202
and she'd eat ice cream
and we'd have her back in two days.

996
01:53:47.327 --> 01:53:49.913
He lied to me!

997
01:53:49.996 --> 01:53:52.874
That's why he's fucking dead!
I did it!

998
01:53:52.999 --> 01:53:55.043
I did it. Lisa!

999
01:53:55.168 --> 01:53:57.879
I agreed to the kidnapping.

1000
01:53:58.004 --> 01:54:01.424
I did it for us...
for the three of us.

1001
01:54:09.891 --> 01:54:11.976
I'm so sorry. Lisa.

1002
01:54:18.024 --> 01:54:19.985
You kill him.

1003
01:54:21.402 --> 01:54:23.280
You kill him or I will.

1004
01:54:53.643 --> 01:54:55.604
Huh. You know. they say a. um...

1005
01:54:58.023 --> 01:55:01.151
a bullet always tells the truth.

1006
01:55:10.452 --> 01:55:12.412
It never lies.

1007
01:55:25.383 --> 01:55:29.638
It didn't work for me. Samuel. but maybe...

1008
01:55:31.932 --> 01:55:34.475
Maybe it'll work for you.

1009
01:55:43.776 --> 01:55:46.404
I'll pray for you.

1010
01:58:48.837 --> 01:58:50.755
- Gracias.

1011
01:59:15.530 --> 01:59:17.448
¿Hola?
Hola.

1012
01:59:17.532 --> 01:59:20.035
- Mr. Creasy?
- Yeah. it's me.

1013
01:59:20.160 --> 01:59:24.205
- I traced the PIN for you and I have an address.
- Yeah?

1014
01:59:24.331 --> 01:59:27.792
The cardholder is Reina Rosas Sanchez.
the wife of “The Voice. "

1015
01:59:27.876 --> 01:59:32.172
She lives in Los Arcos.
apartment 26D. Via Appia.

1016
01:59:32.255 --> 01:59:34.715
- Good.
- And another thing.

1017
01:59:34.841 --> 01:59:38.636
Pick up today's paper and you'll have
a picture of “The Voice. "

1018
01:59:38.720 --> 01:59:40.722
Good. Thank you.

1019
02:00:43.702 --> 02:00:45.787
Shh. shh. shh.

1020
02:01:49.267 --> 02:01:51.186
José? ¿Qué te pasa?

1021
02:03:06.261 --> 02:03:08.096
Sí.

1022
02:03:08.221 --> 02:03:10.181
Okay.

1023
02:03:17.772 --> 02:03:19.524
Hmm?

1024
02:03:26.030 --> 02:03:27.490
Hmm?

1025
02:03:38.585 --> 02:03:40.503
Sí.

1026
02:03:40.587 --> 02:03:42.589
Okay. Uh...

1027
02:03:46.926 --> 02:03:48.845
- ¿Sí?
- Sí.

1028
02:03:56.060 --> 02:03:58.688
Aurelio Rosas Sanchez. Okay.

1029
02:04:03.568 --> 02:04:05.445
Okay.

1030
02:04:13.912 --> 02:04:15.830
Sí.

1031
02:04:15.955 --> 02:04:18.332
Sí.

1032
02:04:18.458 --> 02:04:20.377
Huh?

1033
02:05:17.225 --> 02:05:19.185
Momento.

1034
02:05:48.881 --> 02:05:50.800
Hola.  Daniel.

1035
02:05:50.925 --> 02:05:52.760
Señor Creasy.

1036
02:05:52.885 --> 02:05:56.264
Yeah. Yeah. I got your family here.

1037
02:05:56.347 --> 02:05:58.892
Your brother doesn't look too good.

1038
02:05:59.016 --> 02:06:02.270
Yeah. Reina. she's what.
about eight months?

1039
02:06:02.395 --> 02:06:06.441
Huh? You wanna negotiate?

1040
02:06:10.361 --> 02:06:14.032
The most important thing
in life is family.

1041
02:06:14.115 --> 02:06:16.325
Do you agree?

1042
02:06:17.535 --> 02:06:19.454
I agree.

1043
02:06:21.247 --> 02:06:23.708
And there you are.
You have my family.

1044
02:06:23.791 --> 02:06:26.670
Well. most of my family.

1045
02:06:26.794 --> 02:06:30.924
My wife and I are separated.
You know how that is.

1046
02:06:31.048 --> 02:06:34.803
Now. tell me seriously.
h-how much do you want?

1047
02:06:34.928 --> 02:06:36.680
Ah.

1048
02:06:39.224 --> 02:06:41.726
Your brother wants to speak to you.
Yeah. hold on.

1049
02:06:52.821 --> 02:06:55.949
I'm gonna take your family apart
piece by piece. You understand me?

1050
02:06:56.073 --> 02:06:58.117
- Piece by piece. Shut up!

1051
02:06:59.327 --> 02:07:02.122
I don't want your money!

1052
02:07:02.247 --> 02:07:05.875
Do you understand me?
You understand me? I want you.

1053
02:07:39.033 --> 02:07:41.119
- I'm listening.

1054
02:07:42.537 --> 02:07:45.915
I'm listening. Daniel. I'm listening.

1055
02:07:52.130 --> 02:07:55.424
All right.
I will give you a life for a life.

1056
02:07:57.051 --> 02:07:59.596
Whose life?
What are you talking about?

1057
02:07:59.720 --> 02:08:02.473
Whose life. Daniel? I want you.

1058
02:08:02.557 --> 02:08:06.060
I will give you her life for your life.

1059
02:08:06.186 --> 02:08:10.648
And in exchange.
I will get my life back.

1060
02:08:10.731 --> 02:08:14.735
- What life? Whose life?
- The girl's. Pita's.

1061
02:08:18.657 --> 02:08:22.827
- Pita's dead.
-  Creasy!

1062
02:08:22.910 --> 02:08:28.249
I'm a businessman.
A girl dead is worth nothing. She's alive.

1063
02:08:32.545 --> 02:08:34.547
All right.

1064
02:08:36.466 --> 02:08:38.677
I want proof of life. You hear me?

1065
02:08:38.760 --> 02:08:41.763
I want proof of life.
I want... I want...

1066
02:08:41.846 --> 02:08:44.265
I want the name of her bear.
What does she call her bear?

1067
02:08:44.390 --> 02:08:47.018
You tell her to tell you...

1068
02:08:47.101 --> 02:08:50.646
to tell me what she calls her bear.

1069
02:09:19.425 --> 02:09:22.053
- Yeah?
- Creasy.

1070
02:09:22.136 --> 02:09:25.140
She calls the bear Creasy Bear.

1071
02:09:41.072 --> 02:09:43.033
Okay.

1072
02:09:44.867 --> 02:09:47.454
O-Okay.

1073
02:09:47.578 --> 02:09:50.123
I give you your brother.
you give me the girl.

1074
02:09:51.874 --> 02:09:54.210
- All right.
- Where?

1075
02:10:37.879 --> 02:10:39.798
Hello?

1076
02:10:39.881 --> 02:10:42.550
Lisa. listen to me. Don't hang up.

1077
02:10:42.675 --> 02:10:44.844
I think Pita's alive.

1078
02:10:46.680 --> 02:10:48.890
I can't take this anymore.

1079
02:10:49.015 --> 02:10:50.933
Take the road to Puebla.

1080
02:10:51.017 --> 02:10:53.895
Get off junction 34. south side.

1081
02:10:54.020 --> 02:10:56.022
I'll meet you there in two hours.

1082
02:11:41.359 --> 02:11:43.236
So where is she?

1083
02:11:45.780 --> 02:11:48.908
She's right over there.
You see those two cars out there?

1084
02:11:54.247 --> 02:11:57.500
Pita's kidnapper. Daniel...

1085
02:11:57.625 --> 02:12:00.920
this is his brother.

1086
02:12:02.296 --> 02:12:04.423
Here.

1087
02:12:04.549 --> 02:12:08.261
I'm goin' up on the bridge to get Pita.

1088
02:12:08.386 --> 02:12:11.139
If anything goes wrong.
you put it to his head.

1089
02:12:12.724 --> 02:12:14.851
You pull the trigger. all right?

1090
02:12:15.894 --> 02:12:18.396
You understand?

1091
02:12:21.482 --> 02:12:23.860
You don't...

1092
02:12:23.985 --> 02:12:27.238
Let him loose until she's with you.

1093
02:12:27.321 --> 02:12:29.323
You got it?

1094
02:12:31.785 --> 02:12:34.454
And you don't wait for me. okay?

1095
02:12:37.165 --> 02:12:38.917
Yeah.

1096
02:12:39.000 --> 02:12:42.587
- You'll be all right. You okay?
- Yeah.

1097
02:14:27.776 --> 02:14:29.652
Creasy!

1098
02:14:31.446 --> 02:14:33.406
Creasy!

1099
02:14:34.574 --> 02:14:37.034
Creasy!

1100
02:14:53.301 --> 02:14:55.720
- You all right?
- Yeah.

1101
02:14:55.803 --> 02:14:58.514
They didn't hurt you?

1102
02:14:58.598 --> 02:15:00.975
Hi.

1103
02:15:03.686 --> 02:15:07.982
Your mother's waitin' for you. She's right
down there at the end of the bridge.

1104
02:15:08.108 --> 02:15:11.736
- Okay? You go home.
- Okay.

1105
02:15:11.819 --> 02:15:14.572
- All right.
- Where are you goin'?

1106
02:15:18.451 --> 02:15:20.912
I'm goin' home too.

1107
02:15:21.954 --> 02:15:23.832
I'm goin' to Blue Bayou.

1108
02:15:28.128 --> 02:15:30.755
Oh. Hey.

1109
02:15:30.839 --> 02:15:34.175
I got something for you.

1110
02:15:36.261 --> 02:15:38.263
I got the last number too.

1111
02:15:38.346 --> 02:15:41.182
I love you. Creasy.

1112
02:15:43.685 --> 02:15:46.354
And you love me. don't you?

1113
02:15:47.480 --> 02:15:49.566
Yes. I do.

1114
02:15:49.690 --> 02:15:52.860
- With all my heart. Pita. go.

1115
02:15:52.986 --> 02:15:54.946
- Go. Run.
- Bye.

1116
02:16:08.501 --> 02:16:10.378
¡Vamos!

1117
02:16:10.503 --> 02:16:13.757
- Pita! Baby. come here. It's okay.
- Mom!

1118
02:16:13.881 --> 02:16:17.051
- Mom!
- Come on! Okay. I'll let you go now.

1119
02:16:17.177 --> 02:16:19.220
Mom!

1119
